@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create a new note
POST http://localhost:5001/api/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Note",
  "content": "<h1>Welcome</h1><p>This is my first note with <strong>rich text</strong>!</p>"
}

### Get all notes
GET http://localhost:5001/api/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get a specific note
GET http://localhost:5001/api/notes/NOTE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a note
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/notes/NOTE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "content": "<h1>Updated Content</h1><p>This note has been updated.</p>"
}

### Search notes
GET http://localhost:5001/api/notes/search?q=welcome
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add collaborator
POST http://localhost:5001/api/notes/NOTE_ID_HERE/collaborators
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "collaborator@example.com"
}

### Delete a note (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/notes/NOTE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
